Class RequestForActionAnnotation

org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.surveyaction.properties.Annotation
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.surveyaction.properties.DataFieldAnnotation
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.surveyaction.properties.RequestForActionAnnotation
public class RequestForActionAnnotation extends DataFieldAnnotation
RequestForActionAnnotation is used to record an issue that has been discovered. It is typically used when the survey action service is running quality rules and data values are discovered that are not correct.
